

=Description=

"The purpose of blogging in this case is to record, process and publish data.
The type of data, taken as a gestalt, captures the process as well as the product of learning. The cognitive schema used in a blog post that records and documents these primary sources (original student-created photos, rich pictures and podcasts) to form a more comprehensive, coherent whole, would differ markedly from the schema used to record secondary sources."
